  "runtimeMin": 122,
  "format": "No new wide releases opened, so Sean and Amanda take the movie business's temperature (a fallen Furiosa, a flimsy Garfield, the Fall Guy's VOD math), react to the Wolfs and Venom trailers, and run a book-club check-in. Then the main event: each host drafts a rival movie studio from scratch, picking three filmmakers, five stars, literary properties, a franchise, a classic film, a lot, a windowing plan, and a name. Chris Ryan drops in to have In a Violent Nature described to him, and Sean interviews its writer-director, Chris Nash.",
