          "year": 2024,
          "note": "Down to third in its second weekend; the hosts decide its niche-ness was underrated all along."
        },
        {
          "title": "The Garfield Movie",
          "year": 2024,
          "note": "No. 1 at the box office, which Sean chalks up to the flimsiness of the property."
        },
        {
