          "year": 2024,
          "note": "A good VOD weekend; Amanda argues it simply met its over-35 audience at home."
        },
        {
          "title": "Challengers",
          "year": 2024,
          "note": "Still earning on rental. Sean cites $86.8 million and friends who watched it twice in a morning."
        },
        {
